4637:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h5xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC group regular behavior in case of overrun:
4638:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h5xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         data preserved or overwritten.
