2172:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @note   Possibility to update parameters on the fly:
2173:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         This function initializes multimode parameters, following
2174:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         calls to this function can be used to reconfigure some parameters
2175:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         of structure "ADC_MultiModeTypeDef" on the fly, without resetting
2176:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         the ADCs.
2177:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         The setting of these parameters is conditioned to ADC state.
2178:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         For parameters constraints, see comments of structure
2179:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         "ADC_MultiModeTypeDef".
2180:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @note   To move back configuration from multimode to single mode, ADC must
2181:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         be reset (using function HAL_ADC_Init() ).
2182:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @param hadc Master ADC handle
2183:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @param pMultimode Structure of ADC multimode configuration
2184:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @retval HAL status
2185:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   */
